Sentencas: Ceria-based oxides, such as samaria-doped ceria (SDC), are potential electrolytes for low-to-intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Fe-Doped SDC Solid Solution as an Electrolyte for Low-to-Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The sinterability of these materials can be improved by adding iron as the sintering aid.
Titulo: Fe-Doped SDC Solid Solution as an Electrolyte for Low-to-Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: This work reveals that Fe is soluble in SDC, forming an Fe-doped SDC solid solution.
Titulo: Fe-Doped SDC Solid Solution as an Electrolyte for Low-to-Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: It is found that the solubility is affected by the sintering temperature.
Titulo: Fe-Doped SDC Solid Solution as an Electrolyte for Low-to-Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Fe doping has obvious effects on electrolyte properties, including sintering characteristics, thermal expansion behaviors, and electrical conductivities in both air and hydrogen atmospheres.
Titulo: Fe-Doped SDC Solid Solution as an Electrolyte for Low-to-Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The conductivity obviously increases while the activation energy decreases by doping Fe.
Titulo: Fe-Doped SDC Solid Solution as an Electrolyte for Low-to-Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Compared with that of the bare SDC electrolyte, the performance of the single cell with the Fe-doped SDC is enhanced; for example, the peak power density is increased by 52.8% to 0.726 W cm(-2) at 600 degrees C when humidified hydrogen is used as the fuel and ambient air is used as the oxidant.
Titulo: Fe-Doped SDC Solid Solution as an Electrolyte for Low-to-Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The single cell showed stable operation at 600 degrees C under a constant current density of 0.3 A cm(-2) for 150 h. Therefore, the Fe-doped SDC solid solution shows promise as a potential electrolyte for low-to-intermediate-temperature SOFCs.
Titulo: Fe-Doped SDC Solid Solution as an Electrolyte for Low-to-Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
